purpose: Discuss SEO issues and potential fixes on the HubSpot Platform
text: set the channel description: Discuss SEO issues and potential fixes on the HubSpot Platform

it's a good idea <@U2H3TT8F2> I'm working for a client on a project oriented SEO and discover many limit of HubSpot customization
here are some :
- Some metas are not editable or configurable (author)
- On the sitemap XML on HubSpot the language is forced to EN-us even if the primary language is another one
- One sitemap in HubSpot per domain is limited

There are some key points for SEO that are important and limited on HubSpot (unfortunately)
